latestPosts.caption:
This month is all about knowing your body better and I just had the most insightful experience @bodycraftclinic DLF Phase 1, Gurgaon 

Tried their Body Composition Analysis (BCA) and had a detailed 1:1 with their expert dietitian and fitness coach @singh30tanu and wow, it was eye-opening! It’s not just about weight anymore; it’s about understanding what your body actually needs.

Quick, non-invasive, and so worth it. Highly recommend walking into your nearest Bodycraft Clinic this month for a free BCA. You’ll thank yourself later ✨
Last day of indulgence, royal views, resortwear, hearty breakfast and of course finally a view of The Taj up close. 🤍❤️ Heart is full.
